      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-verdict" id="verdict-41"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-body">
        The EUI-64 process converts a 48-bit MAC address into a 64-bit interface ID by inserting FFFE in the middle and flipping the 7th bit of the first byte.
      </div>
